FRANK E. RUTIG and BRUCE WEBSTER v. LAKE JEM LAND COMPANY, a corporation. 24 So. (2nd) 898

January Term, 1946

February 15, 1946 Division B Walter Warren for appellants. W. H. Poe, Andrews, Lanin & Patterson, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The Court finding no reversible error, the judgment appealed from is affirmed.

It is so ordered.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
